							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/annabelabbsstreets/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/author-photo_annabel-streets_credit-Aaron-Hargreaves-1-100x100.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Annabel Abbs-Streets" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/annabelabbsstreets/">Annabel Abbs-Streets</a></h6>
										Annabel Abbs-Streets is the author of 7 books of fiction, memoir and non-fiction. Her work has been translated into 30 languages. She lives in London and Sussex, in England.																			</div>
